divs: Sighting Detailstaken around 7 pm during a sever t-storm that produced heavy wind, huge hail, extreme rain in spots . never saw the object by naked eye. only when i downloaded pic could i see it . one of the pics it is hard to spot because it changed height and local. there is one more pic to upload but no space on this form . nope not the moon and no dust or debris on my lens. if you want i can print the group of 19 or burn them to a disc in order that they were taken.
